OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1772986287
OL,3,CFour arrested on suspicion of spying
OL,4,Con Jewish community for Iran
OL,6,FFour men have been arrested on
OL,7,Fsuspicion of spying on locations and
OL,8,Findividuals linked to the Jewish
OL,9,Fcommunity for Iran.
OL,11,FThe Metropolitan Police said the
OL,12,Fsuspects, one Iranian and three dual
OL,13,FBritish-Iranian nationals, have been
OL,14,Ftaken into custody on suspicion of
OL,15,Fassisting a foreign intelligence
OL,16,Fservice.
OL,18,FThe force said the men, aged 22, 40,
OL,19,F52 and 55, were arrested at addresses
OL,20,Fin Harrow, Watford and Barnet shortly
OL,21,Fafter 1am on Friday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/4
