OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1772986287
OL,3,CFour arrested on suspicion of spying
OL,4,Con Jewish community for Iran
OL,6,FCommander Helen Flanagan, Head of
OL,7,FCounter Terrorism Policing London,
OL,8,Fconfirmed the arrests are "part of a
OL,9,Flong-running investigation".
OL,11,FShe added: "We understand the public
OL,12,Fmay be concerned, in particular the
OL,13,FJewish community, and as always, I
OL,14,Fwould ask them to remain vigilant and
OL,15,Fif they see or hear anything that
OL,16,Fconcerns them, then to contact us."
OL,18,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,19,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,20,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,21,Finbox every Friday morning.
