OL,3,CFour arrested on suspicion of spying
OL,4,Con Jewish community for Iran
OL,6,FThe Met said the arrests follow the
OL,7,Falleged surveillance of locations and
OL,8,Findividuals in the Jewish community in
OL,9,FLondon.
OL,11,FSearches are ongoing at the addresses
OL,12,Fwhere the suspects were arrested by
OL,13,Fcounter-terrorism officers, as well as
OL,14,Fadditional properties in Wembley and
OL,15,FBarnet.
OL,17,FSix other men were also arrested in
OL,18,FHarrow on suspicion of assisting an
OL,19,Foffender and have been taken into
OL,20,Fcustody, the force said.
